"registros capturados."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:316
msgid ""
"Click the :icon:`fa-bars` :guilabel:`Records` smart button to :ref:`manage "
"these records <data_cleaning/recycle>`."
msgstr ""
"Clique no botão inteligente :icon:`fa-bars` :guilabel:`Registros` "
