"work_with_data/functions>`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet.rst:28
msgid ":doc:`insert and link to Odoo data <spreadsheet/insert>`"
msgstr ":doc:`inserir e vincular aos dados do Odoo <spreadsheet/insert>`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet.rst:29
msgid ":doc:`use pivot tables <spreadsheet/work_with_data/pivot_tables>`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet.rst:30
msgid ""
"filter data across multiple Odoo data sources using :doc:`global filters "
