#~ "entrada de todos os seus seguidores) pelo alias catchall (** catchall @ "
#~ "**)."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "**Bounced messages** are routed to **bounce@** in order to track them in "
#~ "Odoo. This is especially used in `Odoo Email Marketing <https://"
#~ "www.odoo.com/page/email-marketing>`__ to opt-out invalid recipients."
